# Docker build context for reticulum-integ/Dockerfile is the repo root, but
# the image only needs reticulum-integ/entrypoint.sh (RNS is installed from
# PyPI). Without this file the context was the whole tree (~3.5 GB, dominated
# by target/), shipped to the daemon on every per-scenario `compose up
# --build` — making bring-up slow and variable enough to blow heavy scenarios'
# timeouts under the full sequential suite. Excluding build output keeps the
# context to a few KB so `up` is fast and deterministic.
target/
.git/
reticulum-integ/logs/
**/*.log
**/*.deb
docs/book/
